FBIS4-55403 "dreeu094_h_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-094 Daily Report 13 May 1994 HUNGARY Head of TV News, Election Program Resigns Head of TV News, Election Program Resigns LD1305174094 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network in Hungarian 1600 GMT 13 May 94 LD1305174094 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network Hungarian BFN [Text] Laszlo Juhasz, news director for Hungarian television and head of the election programs office, has resigned. He informed Deputy Chairman Gabor Nahlik of his decision on 7 May, one day before the first round of the National Assembly elections. Nahlik accepted the resignation. Laszlo Juhasz recalled that last November he accepted the position of director of news only temporarily, until the conclusion of the National Assembly elections.
